==English==

===Noun===
'''diameter''' (''plural'' '''[[diameters]]''')

#{{geometry}} Any [[straight line]] between two points on the [[circumference]] of a [[circle]] that passes through the [[centre]]/[[center]] of the circle.
#{{geometry}} The length of such a line.

